<h1>Create All Shifts</h1>

<!-- defaulting to helpdesk for now -->
<h2>Make sure to double check the <%= link_to "lab times", edit_lab_path(@lab) %> </h2>

<!-- 

Beginning Semester
last day of shifts for the regularly scheduled semester
last day of shifts for entire semester


